description: Guidelines for using REST API with TanStack Query
globs: src/**/*.tsx
---
- Use generated API client functions when available
- Use TanStack Query (useQuery, useMutation) for all API calls
- Use consistent query key patterns
- Handle loading and error states from TanStack Query
- Use queryClient.invalidateQueries after mutations to sync state
- Use optimistic updates for better UX when appropriate
- Follow REST API error handling patterns
